{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Hoodwinked_Baron",
  "title": "The Hoodwinked Baron",
  "summary": "On a neon-lit skyhook casino over Nar Shaddaa, a con crew works the exiled Rattataki Baron Songir Fentrus, who is recruiting mercenaries to retake his stolen holding. The grifter Aisaiy, posing as a newly divorced heiress named Cieeve in a striking red dress, lures the lecherous Baron's full attention while her partners move into position: the mercenary captain Sorin, playing \"Lothor,\" with his fake slave-girl bodyguard Suana, and the Twi'lek hostess Chez'na, while the Baron's harried yeoman Valya manages his assets. Aisaiy steers the gloating Baron to Sorin's sabacc table, where Suana secretly signals Sorin's play through gestures of affection, and the crew bleads the Baron into ever-higher stakes, ultimately winning a freighter off him with false assets. As the Baron realizes he has been cheated, Aisaiy distracts him with food and a feigned upset stomach to cover the crew's escape, but the furious Baron quietly dispatches his Weequay security chief to ambush Sorin at the hangar and recover the incriminating datapad.",
